      • getOptions

        Options getOptions(Scope scope)
        Gets scoped options of this configurable instance.

        Note that the implementation specifies whether this method returns a snapshot or view of options.

        Parameters:
        scope - the scope to be applied, not null
        Returns:
        either a snapshot or view of options
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if an unknown scope is specified
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if the scope is null
